messages.content:
%You awaken to the sound of an alarm blaring. The room around you is small and cramped. You are in your bunk on the USS Buttknuckle. Cal's voice can be heard over the intercom, telling everyone to report to the bridge immediately. You can hear footsteps rushing past your door.% 

{What do you do?}

1. Get dressed and head to the bridge
2. Stay in bed and ignore the alarm
3. Look around the room for anything useful
{ Something else }
